    "description": {
      "zh": "跳蚤市场: 1₽ | 物品价值: 1 | Peacekeeper报价: 0₽似乎没有必要解读纸条上写的“Ark”到底是什么意思，显然更接近某种密码或者暗号。Polikhim化工厂的地下通道内有不少上锁的门，通向错综复杂的地道网络。如果报出正确的暗号，说不定会有人开门放行。",
      "en": "跳蚤市场: 1₽ | 物品价值: 1 | Peacekeeper报价: 0₽The word “Ark” hardly needs to be taken literally. It's more like a code word. There are quite a few locked doors under the Polikhim Factory, leading deeper into the catacombs. Perhaps someone will open the door for you if you know the code word."
